      "detail": "AI-assisted generation means language models produce the synthetic interactions that constitute synthetic exhaust. The AI tools create plausible conversation patterns, preference signals, and feedback data that resemble authentic user interactions. AI assistance enables exhaust manufacturing at scale and quality levels that human content farms alone could not achieve. AI-generated synthetic exhaust is the self-referential irony where AI tools undermine the data market they created."
    },
